      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Flooded Forest Fiasco",
        "Client": "Teary-eyed Boy",
        "Description": "*sniff* Papa promised we\u0027d go\r\nfishin\u0027 \u0027cuz I was a good boy, I did\r\nall my chores. Brushed my teeth.\r\nEven cleaned my room! But now\r\nwe can\u0027t *sniff* because *sniff*\r\na bunch of dumb monsters. *sob*\r\nIt\u0027s not fair! *sniff*",
